description:
Danny interviews Teddi Mellencamp, the newest cast member on The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills. She talks about joining the cast, her rockstar dad, her favorite Meg Ryan movie, and lots more. Danny also breaks down #PumpRules and Molly's Game with actor/writer/straight, Sean Crampton. 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
